      "content": "that's what i thought. it feels way too specific to be just \"personalization\" though. like, it's not just playing different music, it's the lighting getting dimmer when i'm feeling down or the heat rising when i'm getting agitated. do you think they're running some kind of psychological trial on me or something? like using my own house to see how certain environmental shifts affect my mood?",
